title: Frigidaire 30in Freestanding Gas Range FFGF3016
description:
Frigidaire Black Freestanding Gas Range - FFGF3016TB

Features:

Sealed Gas Burners 
Enjoy easier cleanup and a burner that stays looking great

Built with American Pride 
Designed, engineered and assembled in the U.S.A.

Broil and Serve Drawer 
Easily toast, brown, or crisp the outside of your food at the touch of a button

Low Simmer Burner
Perfect for cooking delicate foods and sauces

Color-Coordinated Oven Door with Extra-Large Window
Our extra-large oven window makes it easier to check on the status of your dish without having to open the oven door

Electronic Kitchen Timer 
Times up to 12 hours
